= All Power to the Soviets

All power to the soviets. 

@2nd_soviet
go-to: 2nd_soviet_menu

Having seized power from the Provisional Government, we must now decide on a replacement. Though some assumed the Soviet Executive would simply absorb the functions of the government, the Bolsheviks have arranged for the creation of a "temporary" auxiliary organ to perform similar duties: the **Council of People's Commissars** (Sovnarkom). 

There is general support among the delegates and parties, including from a sizeable minority of our own party (**Bolshevik Moderates**), for the creation of a broad socialist coalition government. However, the **Leninists** of our party view this as untenable, and have successfully strongarmed the Bolshevik Moderates into going along with this (at least as a start). Hypothetically, we could offer a handful of seats to sympathetic non-Bolshevik leaders, but it's unlikely any would accept. Even the Left SRs, though sympathetic to our actions in general, have announced they will stand firm on an all-socialist government. Therefore, Lenin is prepared to present a list for an exclusively Bolshevik composition. 

@2nd_soviet_menu

- @2nd_soviet_bolshevik: Form an exclusively Bolshevik government.
- @2nd_piecemeal: Offer some piecemeal concessions to sympathetic groups. 
- @2nd_soviet_homogenous: Form a genuinely all-socialist government. 

